Class LfAdjustAlgorithmImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl
          org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
LfAdjustAlgorithm, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
public class LfAdjustAlgorithmImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements LfAdjustAlgorithm

An implementation of the model object 'Lf Adjust Config'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Apply Adjust Algo
  • Activate All Adjust
  • Voltage Adjust
  • Pv Limit Adjust Only
  • Volt Adj Start Point
  • Volt Adj Tolerance Factor
  • Voltage Adj App Type
  • Power Adjust
  • Power Adj Start Point
  • Power Adj App Type
  • Limit Backoff Check
  • Discrete VAdjust
  • Lf Algo

needAdjustment

public boolean needAdjustment()
Check if there is a need to perform adjustment. It deligates the decision to the LfAdjustAlgorithm and NetAdjustAlgorithm. The info is used when checking LF convergence. The actual adjustment might be delayed depending on adjustment implementation.

Specified by:
needAdjustment in interface LfAdjustAlgorithm

doAllAdjust

public void doAllAdjust(Mismatch mismatch,
                        AclfMethod lfMethod)
Perform adjustment. It delegates the action to the LfAdjustAlgorithm and NetAdjustAlgorithm. Rules may be implement to determine when the adjustment might be performed. This method is called at the beginning of each NR/PQ/GS iteration

Specified by:
doAllAdjust in interface LfAdjustAlgorithm
